{"tid":2259676,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大市場大民意 更有效抗衡中共","createTime":"2020-10-27T04:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T04:15:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a3586fe58870d4b585476460356e7ca1b7f19a01","tid":2259676,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T04:15:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201027/2IQL7YM7SJHFFILC2NOA63WP6Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201027%2F2IQL7YM7SJHFFILC2NOA63WP6Q%2F&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETVDf25aqCgCAAhwKlvpwqyI%3D&h=dd6c8736\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201027%2F2IQL7YM7SJHFFILC2NOA63WP6Q%2F&h=b16cd1ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201027/2IQL7YM7SJHFFILC2NOA63WP6Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n大市場大民意 更有效抗衡中共<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wUzFLHuR4SCss4iEiLXvuY2_o_U=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CSE3HCML5FGCLNA5RUUTQX5FVA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwUzFLHuR4SCss4iEiLXvuY2_o_U%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCSE3HCML5FGCLNA5RUUTQX5FVA.jpg&h=de134f82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中天支持者一度與警方推撞。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n拆局<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：NCC專家斥報道偏頗 查證不足  中天續牌聽證 蔡衍明發飆<br />\n<br />\n中天續牌事實引起全台灣關注，藍綠兩陣營的意見兩極化。台大新研所教授洪貞玲認為，蔡衍明的問題在於無法讓人信服他沒有介入中天的新聞編採，昨日更以「溝通」等文眼模糊帶過，給予外界很大想像空間。時事評論員劉銳紹認為，抗衡中共的意識形態，最好的方法是用大市場、大民意，而不是用大陸的方法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與主管溝通疑介入編採<br />\n<br />\n洪貞玲認為，在於蔡衍明接手集團之後，媒體也報道過蔡向大陸提交報告的相關新聞，造。。。。。。。。。。。。給予外界很大想像空間，何況溝通也不一定要進辦公室，相信外界與委員都已經聽到，也會有所評價。<br />\n<br />\n「中共利用人哋嘅民主自由，來擴大自己嘅影響力，其實呢點中外古今。。。。。。。。。。。。府宜用大市場、大民意去抗衡意識形態的入侵，而不是用大陸的方法去打壓。"}]}